**Nightingale** series (also known as _Rose chart_, _Wind Rose_, _Polar area_, _Coxcomb chart_) represents a dataset in the form of a polar area diagram.

## Single Series

To create a basic Nightingale chart, use a data array where each item has one category value (for the angle axis) and one numeric value (for the radius axis).

A minimal Nightingale series configuration will look like:

```js
series: [
    {
        type: 'nightingale',
        angleKey: 'product',
        radiusKey: 'sales',
    },
];
```

